{"tid":826162,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】開開Power Rangers Day254 18/9","createTime":"2018-09-18T05:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:52:51.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9baab38506b2d3a3a807dc5efbee62b2c327094","tid":826162,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我通常於晚上11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=cc62d0e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=77f9ba15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"e51c76558d0ebbf72dfa3e6750508124e93c9f80","tid":826162,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce372cef111619b3ab28258edc91432179229c70","tid":826162,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ff4777e53d036db0a360a2f38074f2403022cc","tid":826162,"uid"